{"tid":115130,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"中文叻既人真係好吸引","createTime":"2017-02-10T10:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T05:07:43.000Z","uid":27200,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6414a4a471fdc723c969b5a3e64e2934310ffa98","tid":115130,"uid":27200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:37:19.000Z","msg":"雖然d人成日話中文系等丐食又唔知讀咩<br />\n但對於一d對中國文學有濃厚興趣既人<br />\n我好欣賞佢地<br />\n文筆好既人可以將一段故事 經歷寫得栩栩如生<br />\n甚至將成個意境寫入隻歌到<br />\n=======================================<br />\n弱水三千<br />\n<br />\n作詞：林夕<br />\n作曲：馮穎琪<br />\n編曲：張亞東<br />\n監製：麥浚龍、Jerald<br />\n<br />\n三千春江水　暫住寂寞天空<br />\n逛夠了世界　撇進了春風<br />\n<br />\n＊活著自活著　萬象在逝水中暢泳<br />\n　偶爾愛上過　一些倒影<br />\n　流連流成河流留過幾道名勝<br />\n　浪停下像拿著鏡　難辨舊日風景<br />\n　山水非山水　凍了變雪堆<br />\n　山水般山水　遇熱若霧水<br />\n　混雜絕望後便是淚水衍生出心碎<br />\n　狂濤約花絮 醉了愛再醉<br />\n　會跌進漩渦太虛<br />\n　擠於渠裡　浸於浴裡<br />\n　同樣落自春水<br />\n<br />\n＃汗滴在血海紅不紅<br />\n　散聚後味道餘殘濃不濃<br />\n<br />\n　那是快感還是痛<br />\n　深海裡永遠看不通<br />\n　靜靜地浮游在青空<br />\n　一轉身可以化進了杯中<br />\n　口乾了便喝盡那密雲<br />\n　像喝掉如夢如幻信不信<br />\n<br />\nRepeat　＊＃<br />\n女聲：三千春江水　暫住寂寞天空<br />\n　　　逛夠了世界　撇進了春風<br />\n　　　(清水苦水一樣暫住半空)<br />\n　　　水中不起花　萬物靜默不動<br />\n　　　碎了這塊鏡　照見了洶湧　眉頭才震動<br />\n<br />\nRepeat　＃<br />\n女聲：水慢慢　飄色於天空<br />\n　　　水慢慢　將萬物玩弄<br />\n<br />\n活著若是夢　是夢蝶讓水色震動<br />\n撇夠了冷雨　得到青空<br />\n=======================================<br />\n林夕d詞真係好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/mw690/005yNs0Bgw1ewmry3p1rcj30no0zkjtw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F005yNs0Bgw1ewmry3p1rcj30no0zkjtw.jpg&h=812dec6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1581539-49858a8356e0cffc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload-images.jianshu.io%2Fupload_images%2F1581539-49858a8356e0cffc.jpg&h=733f63d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林夕 ─ 1984年畢業於香港大學文學院中文系，主修翻譯。"},{"pid":"acaea51ff94e3fe7a70aa0b01d66f34825e352b8","tid":115130,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0d80dc5ec7496734909dfd798006c5a6e1e4ad","tid":115130,"uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"覺 見到啲人用詞好靚 成個意境出晒黎就好想追住佢地黎含<br />\n但現實係中文叻不及英文叻"},{"pid":"c813683b99acf7774fd1df30e1ce88fb1ba70c7b","tid":115130,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:39:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"824e2d330492a2cbd5f732c27e6d1c1fe38af4c6","tid":115130,"uid":74547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:41:21.000Z","msg":"其實中文好同讀中文系係無咩關係"},{"pid":"d1da1d209589a671c9d11bccf6913b38ea57c0a8","tid":115130,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T19:05:33.000Z","msg":"中文叻都唔一定做到林夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8472e7b46c6c09ac81fad9a12e938b3492948f8d","tid":115130,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T19:13:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實中文好同讀中文系係無咩關係</blockquote><br />\n其實點為之中文好都有排講"},{"pid":"82deb650169ef2152c70df055c90c57762dcf7ff","tid":115130,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T19:18:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺 見到啲人用詞好靚 成個意境出晒黎就好想追住佢地黎含<br />\n但現實係中文叻不及英文叻</blockquote><br />\nAgger.<br />\nChinese is MK Language.</blockquote><br />\n如果你係以實用性黎講<br />\n中文的確係比唔起上英文<br />\n而世界上亦無邊種語言可以係呢方面比得上英文<br />\n至於搵唔搵到食就睇你有幾叻啦"},{"pid":"6a1f5db274b6a19cbb74340ec867cfeca06e1695","tid":115130,"uid":74876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T19:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺 見到啲人用詞好靚 成個意境出晒黎就好想追住佢地黎含<br />\n但現實係中文叻不及英文叻</blockquote><br />\nAgger.<br />\nChinese is MK Language.</blockquote><br />\n如果你係以實用性黎講<br />\n中文的確係比唔起上英文<br />\n而世界上亦無邊種語言可以係呢方面比得上英文<br />\n至於搵唔搵到食就睇你有幾叻啦</blockquote><br />\nsad but true <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73d375dc278ec784aeb42802f383647e3221fa2","tid":115130,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T19:43:17.000Z","msg":"中文系分文學同經學，如琢如磨，如切如磋，創作出好作品必須有豐富既閱讀基礎。<br />\n<br />\n利申中文系grad乞緊食，有無野幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eaa8bdf35d01af68ab6c28aaca072aad0e0fda1","tid":115130,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T20:25:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b66682b92a562a7d8372af44308c15821a81651e","tid":115130,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T20:31:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31c74b7a5b2ce8522d633919f30bdc83bec00a00","tid":115130,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T20:44:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5032e52e0fd01ab2e118c9e38d6a643178b48a15","tid":115130,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T21:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中文系分文學同經學，如琢如磨，如切如磋，創作出好作品必須有豐富既閱讀基礎。<br />\n<br />\n利申中文系grad乞緊食，有無野幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申理學院minor咗經學<br />\n準備MA經學排隊乞食<br />\n無野幫到大家 我出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680876209d20ee28a4e3e413c6c338a48800a570","tid":115130,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:07:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺 見到啲人用詞好靚 成個意境出晒黎就好想追住佢地黎含<br />\n但現實係中文叻不及英文叻</blockquote><br />\nAgger.<br />\nChinese is MK Language.</blockquote><br />\n如果你係以實用性黎講<br />\n中文的確係比唔起上英文<br />\n而世界上亦無邊種語言可以係呢方面比得上英文<br />\n至於搵唔搵到食就睇你有幾叻啦</blockquote><br />\nChinese is easy to learn but easy to abuse.<br />\nSo it is very difficult to master.<br />\nEnglish is just the opposite.<br />\nEven you master Chinese you have to comply with PRC's shit norms (e.g. 打造 XXX, 專注研究)</blockquote><br />\n第一次覺得龜仔講野係有道理"}]}